{
  "info": {
    "name": "OrByte API",
    "description": "Colección completa de pruebas para la API REST de OrByte.\n\nPre-requisitos:\n1. Servidor Django corriendo: python manage.py runserver\n2. Datos cargados: python manage.py seed_db\n3. Ejecutar los 3 requests de Login — los tokens se guardan automáticamente.\n\nVariables de colección:\n- base_url → http://localhost:8000\n- token_admin / token_vendedor / token_cliente → se llenan al hacer login\n- pedido_id → ID de un pedido en estado Registrado (default 36, el último del seed)\n- importacion_id → ID de una importación para eliminar (actualizar tras importar)\n\nIDs del seed (BD limpia):\n  Usuarios: Carlos(admin)=1 | María(vend)=2 | Luis(vend)=3 | Juan(cli)=4 | Ana=5 | Pedro=6 | Sofía=7 | Andrés=8\n  Productos: MX Keys=1 | MX Master=2 | BlackWidow=3 | DeathAdder=4 | Kraken=5 | Alloy Origins=6 | Pulsefire=7 | Cloud Alpha=8\n  Estados: Registrado=1 | En preparación=2 | Enviado=3 | Completado=4 | Cancelado=5\n  Marcas: Logitech=1 | Razer=2 | HyperX=3\n  Categorías: Teclados=1 | Mouses=2 | Diademas=3",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",       "value": "http://localhost:8000" },
    { "key": "token_admin",    "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_vendedor", "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_cliente",  "value": "" },
    { "key": "pedido_id",      "value": "36" },
    { "key": "importacion_id", "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "1. Autenticación",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login — Admin (Carlos Rodríguez)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var r = pm.response.json(); if (r.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token_admin', r.token);"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@orbyte.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/login/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","login",""] },
            "description": "Esperado 200. El token se guarda automáticamente en token_admin."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Vendedor (María García)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var r = pm.response.json(); if (r.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token_vendedor', r.token);"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"maria.g@orbyte.com\",\n  \"password\": \"trab1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/login/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","login",""] },
            "description": "Esperado 200. Token guardado en token_vendedor.\nAlternativa: luis.f@orbyte.com / trab1234"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Cliente (Juan Pérez)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var r = pm.response.json(); if (r.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token_cliente', r.token);"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"cliente1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/login/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","login",""] },
            "description": "Esperado 200. Token guardado en token_cliente.\nOtros clientes: ana@gmail.com | pedro@gmail.com | sofia@gmail.com | andres@gmail.com — todos usan contraseña cliente1234"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — ERROR credenciales inválidas → 400",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@orbyte.com\",\n  \"password\": \"contraseña_incorrecta\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/login/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","login",""] },
            "description": "Esperado 400."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Token {{token_admin}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/logout/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","logout",""] },
            "description": "Invalida el token activo. Cambiar el header para cerrar sesión con otro rol.\nEsperado 200: { \"message\": \"Sesión cerrada.\" }"
          }
        }
      ]
    },

